---
title: Easy Tex-Mex Baked Chicken with Zesty Roast Veggie & Crispy Flatbread Toss
description: Try a taste of Tex-Mex cuisine with a difference! We're giving golden veggies and baby spinach a flavour boost with tender chicken rubbed with mild spices. Add a dollop of smokey aioli and crispy flatbreads for a feast worthy of a fiesta!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
